@customFieldsId=

### Retrieves all custom fields in an account
get {{hostname}}/api/account/customfields
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{api}}

### Updates an account custom field or Adds a custom field to an account
put {{hostname}}/api/account/customfields
//post {{hostname}}/api/account/customfields
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{api}}

