### Retrieves an account specified custom field
get {{hostname}}/api/account/customfields/{{customFieldsId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{api}}

## Deletes an account custom field by its ID
delete {{hostname}}/api/account/customfields/{{customFieldsId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{api}}
